            "title": "代码高亮测试",
            "date_published": "2021-01-18T07:34:55.138Z",
            "content_html": "<p>SPI ，全称为 Service Provider Interface，是一种服务发现机制。在 ClassPath 路径下的 META-INF/services 文件夹查找文件，自动加载文件里所定义的类。</p>\n<a id=\"more\"></a>\n<h2 id=\"\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#\">#</a> </h2>\n<hr>\n<pre class=\"highlight\"><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"string\">&lt;figure</span> <span class=\"string\">class=&quot;highlight</span> <span class=\"string\">yaml&quot;&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"string\">&lt;table&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"string\">&lt;tbody&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"string\">&lt;tr&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"string\">&lt;td</span> <span class=\"string\">class=&quot;gutter&quot;&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"string\">&lt;pre&gt;&lt;span</span> <span class=\"string\">class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"string\">&lt;/td&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"string\">&lt;td</span> <span class=\"string\">class=&quot;code&quot;&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"string\">&lt;pre&gt;&lt;span</span> <span class=\"string\">class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;&lt;span</span> <span class=\"string\">class=&quot;attr&quot;&gt;hello:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span</span> <span class=\"string\">class=&quot;string&quot;&gt;hexo&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"string\">&lt;/td&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"string\">&lt;/tr&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"string\">&lt;/tbody&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"string\">&lt;/table&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"string\">&lt;/figure&gt;</span></span><br></pre>\n<pre class=\"highlight\"><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"attr\">hello:</span> <span class=\"string\">hexo</span></span><br></pre>",
